The Rolling Stones
Valle Hovin, Oslo, Norway
August 7th 1990

LINEAGE:
Tape source (most probably 1st or 2nd gen) -> Falo -> Denom DRM 540 tape deck -> PC -> FLAC (EAC) -> You

QUALITY:
G-VG audience

COMMENTS:
OK, so here it is. The 2nd Oslo show of 1990 in G-VG quality. As far as I know, this show hasn't been up on torrent-trackers before.
Recieved the tapes in mid 90s, from a person who said he had a 1st gen copy.
The 1990 shows in Oslo were the first Rolling Stones concerts in Norway since 1965, and was also my first Rolling Stones concert

ARTWORK:
It's an honour to have Mr. D making artwork for this. He is certainly the best artwork-creator in Rolling Stones land

Thanks to Falo for transferring the tapes I sent him.
No changes has been made to the sound.

Tape source: ErikSnow
